---
description: "Add a new tool to enforce-uv.sh"
argument-hint: "tool-name"
allowed-tools: ["Read", "Edit"]
---

Add {{$1}} to the enforce-uv.sh script.

Current file: @~/.claude/hooks/enforce-uv.sh

1. Read the current UV_TOOLS array
2. Add {{$1}} to the list (alphabetically)
3. Update the file
4. Confirm the tool is added

Example tools to add:
- ipython
- jupyter
- sphinx-build
- pre-commit
- twine

After adding, {{$1}} will be automatically prefixed with `uv run`.